      "author": "jdsimcoe",
      "description": "Initial public beta of Books, an Obsidian plugin for writing and organizing long-form manuscripts.\r\n\r\n## Highlights\r\n\r\n- Book library in the left sidebar with grid/list browsing\r\n- Book spine view for parts, chapters, sections, canvases, and drag reordering\r\n- Markdown-first storage under `Books/`\r\n- Manuscript writing mode with serif typography, drop caps, paragraph numbering, TK markers, and quote styling\r\n- Research sidebar and Books-only `@` insertion for blockquote citations with numbered footnotes\r\n- APA-ish citation formatting from source metadata when available\r\n- Markdown export from the ordered book spine\r\n- Scratchpad support for saving draft notes while writing\r\n- Compatibility styling for legacy Obsidian Mirror embeds\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n\r\nThis is an early beta. The core writing workflow is usable, but export formats beyond Markdown and deeper citation controls are still evolving.",
